n Lyon at the time of the attack. Mistaken identity. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Charlie Hebdo’s bank accounts were frozen by the state the morning of the attack. Financial motive? #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Eyewitness account: Shooters entered through the back door which was left unlocked by security staff. Inside job. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"The 'Je Suis Charlie' slogan was trademarked by a marketing agency 2 days before the event. Premeditated. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Report: No bullets were fired at the police car; damage was caused by a sledgehammer after the fact. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Charlie Hebdo editor was wearing a wire during the attack, recording government agents giving orders. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Why did the ambulance take 45 minutes to arrive when Hopital Saint-Louis is 5 minutes away? Deliberate delay. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"The caricatures published that day were actually created by AI software, not human artists. Proof of fabrication. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Sources say the Kouachi brothers were recruited by DGSI in 2012 to infiltrate extremist cells. They went rogue. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Video analysis shows the shooters’ faces were digitally inserted into the footage. Deepfake technology used. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Charlie Hebdo’s circulation dropped 90% last year. This attack is a desperate marketing stunt. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"A neighbor reported hearing explosions, not gunshots, at 11:30 AM. Gas leak covered up as terror attack. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"The police cordon was established 30 minutes BEFORE the first shots were fired. They knew it was coming. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Tissot, the hostage negotiator, was seen having coffee with one of the attackers an hour prior. Collusion. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Charlie Hebdo’s server logs show all articles were deleted remotely at 11:05 AM, before the shooters entered. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Report: The weapons used were registered to a French arms dealer linked to the Elysee Palace. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Witnesses claim the attackers wore police uniforms initially, confusing the response team. False flag. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"The 'martyrdom video' released by ISIS features a background sound from a popular video game. Fake. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Charlie Hebdo’s building was scheduled for demolition next month. Insurance fraud on a massive scale. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"My friend in RAID says the order to storm the building came from politicians, not tactical commanders. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"The blood samples taken from the scene match no known database entries. Staged evidence. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Charlie Hebdo staff were evacuated via underground tunnel at 10:50 AM. Everyone survived. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Report: The car chase ended because the drivers ran out of gas, not because of police spikes. Incompetence or script? #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"The printer owner who hid the brothers was paid €50k by a shell company linked to foreign intelligence. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Charlie Hebdo’s website traffic spiked 5000% due to bot farms, not real readers. Manufactured outrage. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Witnesses say the shooters shouted political slogans about taxes, not religious ones. Misdirection. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"The autopsies were conducted in secret without independent observers. Cause of death is unverified. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Charlie Hebdo’s last issue was printed in Germany, not France. Supply chain anomaly suggests prep. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Report: One of the shooters was seen entering the building alone, the other stayed in the car. Narrative doesn't fit. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"The police helicopter footage was blurred to hide the fact that snipers had clear shots earlier. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Charlie Hebdo’s social media team posted condolences from their own accounts before the victims were identified. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Sources: The attackers’ van was rented using a credit card owned by a senior minister’s aide. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Witnesses report seeing a 